= NicoChanWatcher

Watching new videos in specified channels of NicoNicoDoga for OSX.

= Coding NOW

== Requires
 * rest_client
 * xml_simple
 * ruby-growl

== Config
 * ~/.NicoChanWatcher.yaml
   * To specify your channels.
   * example:
   # Listing channels URL
   - http://ch.nicovideo.jp/channel/yuru # is Full-URL of `yurumeitsu`.
   - nyaruko # is Shortcut of `nyaruko-san`.
